label: uncl1505
comment: Code specifying a type of value list.

values.label: Non coded list
values.comment: The list contains a set of non coded values.

values.label: Date and time list
values.comment: The list contains a set of dates, dates and times, or times.

values.label: Coded list
values.comment: The list contains a set of coded data values.

values.label: Structure correspondence link
values.comment: The list contains a set of correspondence links between structures.

values.label: Structure overlapping link
values.comment: The list contains a set of overlapping link values between structures.

values.label: Structure historic link
values.comment: The list contains a set of historic link values between structures.

values.label: Structure hierarchical link
values.comment: The list contains a set of hierarchical link values between structures.

values.label: Structure group link
values.comment: The list contains a set of group link values between structures.

values.label: Multiple hierarchical structure item
values.comment: The list contains a set of items at multiple hierarchical levels in a structure.

values.label: Classification domain
values.comment: The list contains a set of items from a classification domain.

values.label: Single hierarchical structure item
values.comment: The list contains a set of items at a single hierarchical level in a structure.
